data.description: Beautiful Updated 2 story home w/ possibly up to 3600sq ft of living space. across from Lake Holiday! Open concept w/ Fantastic Kitchen Wide Open to Rec room. Granite counter tops, Farm house style sink with high rise faucet & big triple window views.Giant Granite breakfast bar Island Plank Vinyl floors extending into the large Rec room w/ Fireplace and Lake views. Big living room open to formal dining room all w/ Vinyl Plank Flooring. Upper level has three large bedrooms & office that could be possible 4th bedroom.Main bedroom has walk in closet, Ensuite with whirlpool tub with tile surround & attached office w/ walkout to giant upper level deck overlooking Lake Holiday.2 Big other bedrooms all with fans and 1 w/ big walkthrough closet.Large unfinished basement with tall open truss ceiling great for additional living space. Great location less than 300 ft. across from Lake Holiday public access lot w/ dockLive the Resort Lifestyle w/ parks, beaches,lakes,golf course,club house & more!
